reviewText: I was really excited when I saw I could buy my favorite kids cartoon on dvd ! However the only downfall is that this dvd doesn't play on my IMac computer :(

Oh my gosh, I almost laughed when I put this video in.  You would have thought I bought it from someone at the barbershop!  This quality is as poor as it gets.  I seriously wonder if someone recorded this with their personal video camera while at the movies.
